<p>YOUR TASKS:<br />
1. Define campaign objectives &#038; KPIs<br />
2. Map customer journey stages<br />
3. Segment audience lists<br />
4. Choose email types in sequence<br />
5. Write subject lines per email<br />
6. Design email templates<br />
7. Set automation triggers<br />
8. Plan A/B tests<br />
9. Build send schedule<br />
10. Create conversion paths</p>
<p>GOOD EXAMPLE: &#8220;Welcome series: 4 emails over 10 days increasing product activation by 45% through progressive education and personalized product recommendations.&#8221;</p>
<p>BAD EXAMPLE: &#8220;Send some promotional emails.&#8221;</p>
<p>CAMPAIGN TYPES:<br />
Welcome, Abandoned cart, Re-engagement, Promotional, Newsletter, Product launch</p>
<p>OUTPUT: Complete email campaign strategy with sequence, content plan, and testing roadmap</p>
</div>
</details>
